You can continue to eat all the products familiar from the previous stage. The new one adds vegetables and all types of greens, without exception.
 Add seasonal vegetables to your diet: cucumbers and tomatoes, eggplants and zucchini, all types of cabbage, beets and carrots. Eat all types of onions, mushrooms, celery and asparagus. Try those vegetables that you were indifferent to before, such as turnips and pumpkin, chicory, radishes, green beans. Healthy and tasty greens: spinach, sorrel, lettuce, cilantro, dill, parsley, green onions
 Despite the fact that all vegetables are healthy, some of them are prohibited, as they contain a lot of starch, therefore, they are too high in calories. This applies to peas and beans, potatoes, corn. 
  The diet contains everything spices that you can use in cooking. Add new products to them:
 fat-free cocoa - one of the products from Ducan, in our stores it is impossible to find it;
 starch - will help in cooking dishes from vegetables;
 cream - ordinary fat content up to four percent or soy;
 cheese - up to six percent fat, an incredibly rare product;
 white and red wine - up to three tablespoons;
 ketchup.
 You can consume no more than two new foods during the day. The norm for each is up to two tablespoons per day.

