Do you want to achieve a result? Then strictly observe the diet, allow yourself exclusively permitted foods and completely refuse any alcoholic beverages. Let's get acquainted in more detail with the list of products that are allowed to be consumed.
 This:  
 - fresh vegetables: lettuce, carrots, tomatoes, parsley and parsnip roots;  
 - green apples;  
 - eggs;  
 - lean fish;  
 - meat products (in priority lean veal, chicken fillet, and also lean beef).  
 From drinks, give preference to coffee, tea and, of course, plain water. It is worth giving up completely from salt and sugar. To give food colors, try adding a little lemon juice to them.
 The Chinese diet provides two (sometimes three) meals. Snacks and lunches are not available. If between the main meals, due to the unusual and limited diet, you feel hunger, try to satisfy it with a cup of unsweetened black coffee or tea.
 Of course, drink in your spare time. from meals time clean water (if you can get thawed - just great). Drinking water costs as much as the body asks for. But it is very desirable that the amount of this liquid necessary for the body be at least 1.5 liters per day. In the hot season, it is recommended to drink 2 liters, because the body loses a lot of fluid (in particular with sweat), and its reserves must be replenished.
